{"tid":2423885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"申領BNO者首超特區護照","createTime":"2021-02-26T07:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:53:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58f1eaee6d4c0ffa2096fd9849d6be40a6d0fa8e","tid":2423885,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/FWTPNBVJWNGCJJKLVORBRO4DLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FFWTPNBVJWNGCJJKLVORBRO4DLE%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd67PkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=d251de14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210226%2FFWTPNBVJWNGCJJKLVORBRO4DLE%2F&h=41e855ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210226/FWTPNBVJWNGCJJKLVORBRO4DLE/</a><br />\n<br />\n申領BNO者首超特區護照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P5iVsmyxnYcjDKV20qfPV4UdxAk=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7DC36V6RQFHPJHBBYA62W5KNX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP5iVsmyxnYcjDKV20qfPV4UdxAk%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7DC36V6RQFHPJHBBYA62W5KNX4.jpg&h=ab75d505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年申請特區護照宗數只有25萬宗，同期英國政府則簽發31萬本BNO護照。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國安法下民心思變，港人申領英國國民（海外）（BNO）護照動力大增。入境處資料顯示，去年只有25萬宗特區護照申請，較前年大跌六成，處方聲稱與疫潮下服務暫停有關；同期英國政府則簽發31萬本BNO護照，是香港主權移交以來，申請特區護照人數首次比BNO少。民主黨前主席劉慧卿指，數字反映港人對香港前景惶恐和擔心，「驚嘅時候咩都拿住喺手」。<br />\n<br />\n據入境處公佈資料，去年申請香港特區護照有250,896宗，較前年跌65.34%；同期簽發的特區護照則有264,877本。入境處解釋，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年入境處大部份辦事處一度停止服務，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自2013至2019年，入境處接獲特區護照申請年均達70萬宗以上；英國2013至2018年間，每年簽發BNO護照數量僅介乎1.5萬至3.7萬本不等，至2019年簽發量則急增至151,600本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉慧卿：反映港人憂前景<br />\n<br />\n入境處去年另接獲209宗變更國籍申請，較前年的289宗略減；但退出中國國籍申請則由前年的207宗增至299宗，申請成為中國公民則由1,638宗銳減至756宗。<br />\n<br />\n關注BNO議題的民主黨前主席劉慧卿相信，港人1997年前申請BNO後無再續領，但眼見香港「勢色唔對」才續領，令數字急增。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然英國政府容許持。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0fe7d8cba53ed10de2187b9b59bdc990f2232135","tid":2423885,"uid":46388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"其實係因為冇得旅行，過左期冇人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab5d48a46f1957ba90161c2746dd4a6b79f88e7","tid":2423885,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0fe7d8cba53ed10de2187b9b59bdc990f2232135","tid":2423885,"uid":46388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"其實係因為冇得旅行，過左期冇人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"係呀 去曬搞中國護照"},{"pid":"a99ab7ece7589d97266ab118298823e418fae99b","tid":2423885,"uid":361751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0fe7d8cba53ed10de2187b9b59bdc990f2232135","tid":2423885,"uid":46388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"其實係因為冇得旅行，過左期冇人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"弱智仔<br />\n<br />\nBNO都係旅行護照啫"},{"pid":"da39b3a6965335ebb0af5eedb3eca41cb5e0e25c","tid":2423885,"uid":292037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99ab7ece7589d97266ab118298823e418fae99b","tid":2423885,"uid":361751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0fe7d8cba53ed10de2187b9b59bdc990f2232135","tid":2423885,"uid":46388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"其實係因為冇得旅行，過左期冇人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"弱智仔<br />\n<br />\nBNO都係旅行護照啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"On9仔 到底你係幾膠先會話係旅行護照 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我去美國開戶口都係用BNO 國籍就係英國國籍"},{